2008;;Hank and Mike;;Canadian;;Matthiew Klinck;;Paolo Mancini, Thomas Michael, Joe Mantegna, Chris Klein;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hank_and_Mike;;Two blue-collar Easter Bunnies get fired and try their hand at an assortment of odd jobs, failing at each. Fighting depression, debt and eventually each other, their lives start to unravel until they realize that without their job they are nothing.